Often when seeking a night out it can be extremely difficult to find the right fit for my temperamental mood, but somehow Franklin Manor’s unique take on night life manages to provide something for everyone. Depending on where I’m at in the night Franklin is able to satiate my desire for a delicious late-night meal, the chill outdoor pre game hangout, or even a coveted bottle service experience with tables anyone would be lucky to sit at. It’s honestly hard to underplay what a diverse crowd you get at this establishment with a staff that works exceptionally hard to provide you the night out that you’ve always wanted. I got to meet some incredible people from all walks of life here and see some incredible events that I just don’t think would have been handled well anywhere else. That’s why Franklin is the perfect mix of an indoor and outdoor venue where I choose to go on the weekend.

If I want some cocktails with some friends in a cool, trendy bar, I don't need to be entertained by drunk patrons on a dance floor looking to be checked out by other patrons. Give me great cocktails, friendly bartenders & servers, & awesome bar food, & I will be back time & time again, no matter how overpriced everything is, like at Franklin Manor.
